# Internationalization (i18n)

The application supports multiple languages through i18next.

## Translation Files
- [frontend/src/i18n/locales/en/translation.json](mdc:frontend/src/i18n/locales/en/translation.json) - English translations
- [frontend/src/i18n/locales/pt/translation.json](mdc:frontend/src/i18n/locales/pt/translation.json) - Portuguese translations

## Language Context
- [frontend/src/presentation/contexts/LanguageContext.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/presentation/contexts/LanguageContext.tsx) - Language context provider

## Usage
```typescript
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';

function MyComponent() {
  const { t } = useTranslation();
  return <div>{t('some.translation.key')}</div>;
}
```

## Available Languages
- English (en)
- Portuguese (pt)

